    "The original system was characterized by basic roles, such as Email Drafter, which failed to address the complexities of supply chain management.",
    "Five specialized roles were introduced to enhance the system, focusing on supply chain analysis, optimization, and sustainability.",
    "This comprehensive approach allowed for a deeper analysis of supply chain challenges and operational inefficiencies.",
    "The evolved agent system demonstrated significant improvements, with enhanced clarity, accuracy, and actionability in outputs.",
    "The modifications led to outputs that exceeded the refined evaluation criteria, establishing the system as a valuable tool for e-commerce companies seeking effective supply chain solutions."
